plot: Abhilash is worried about his General Studies Exam. Dissatisfied with his mentor, he decides to quit his coaching institute.

Having a good teacher is extremely important while preparing for UPSC. Abhilash knows it, but he thinks his teacher is not good enough and wants to leave his current coaching center and find a better one. But his current institute doesn't have a fee-return policy. What will Abhilash do now. Will he continue with his current coaching center or will he find a better teacher.—Youtube
